  "title": "Lab Application Technician",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform routine and non-routine laboratory tests and analyses on Sealents and waterproofing materials in accordance with established procedures, protocols, and safety guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Receive, label, and prepare samples for testing, ensuring accurate identification and handling in line with SOPs.</li>\n  <li>Monitor inventory levels of consumables, and supplies. Coordinate restocking and proper storage of laboratory materials.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Related Diploma/Degree</li>\n  <li>Fresh Graduates welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>On Job Training provided</li>\n</ul>",
